        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/scene_ebola.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository d8b46cb7-3239-4d44-a9d6-cd44de8d2813).Image",
        "Description": "Hello 47,\r\rWe have four targets for you today, three of whom are witnesses to various top secret ICA operations. These three individuals are working with prominent lawyer Salvatore Bravuomo, who plans to reveal the existence of the ICA to the world. Luckily for us 47, these four targets lack a good amount of security surrounding them, relying on their ability to hide in the Sapienza cityscape. \r\rThis should be an easy job 47, although the existence of these targets is problematic in of itself.",
